reviewText: One of the funniest movies ever!
great movie  great copy  fast service
Has Victoria Abril ever made a bad movie?  FRENCH TWIST, TIE ME UP TIE ME DOWN, Victoria Abril is to live and die for.

Josiane Blasko and Victoria Abril..brilliant together...the eternal triangle is reconfigured,distorted,deconstructed,reconstructed ...Abril as the neglected housewife paying back on the philandering husband who smoulders with jealousy when Abril gets entangled with Blasko; Blasko gets jealous of the husband;Abril gets jealous of Blasko...extremely well acted relationships story that will leave you smiling...
